{"id": 3092, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年有哪些事让你感觉“自己好像跟这个时代脱节了”？", "description": "盘点下新的一年，哪些微妙的事物给你带来了“自己不属于这个时代”的困顿感。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 2068, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201912162231389RCF5d7MbrUij6hz.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-16T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 351235, "content": "网红？明星？傻傻分不清楚！银幕上一张张完美的脸，但我不知道他是谁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675941}, {"id": 350732, "content": "结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1539772}, {"id": 350733, "content": "听歌的口味已经好久没变了", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339105}, {"id": 350737, "content": "歌曲 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607585}, {"id": 350738, "content": "广告上的人都不认识是谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 424, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373628}, {"id": 350739, "content": "很想再拿起毛笔写写字了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713507}, {"id": 350740, "content": "好多新科技不会操作", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1610348}, {"id": 350742, "content": "又熬了一罐猪油", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1044540}, {"id": 350743, "content": "做了奶爸，兄弟们都好久不见了～(o^^o)", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473258}, {"id": 350745, "content": "某某和某某官宣离婚了，我一脸懵逼，这TM都是谁跟谁？", "image": null, "praise_count": 310, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215971}, {"id": 350746, "content": "只是单纯与流行文化脱节了，真正艰深的那些知识还一直保持通信。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565525}, {"id": 350747, "content": "这又是谁啊，干啥了，关我啥事啊，干嘛给我推送啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 188, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135562}, {"id": 351005, "content": "抖肩舞……没懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311736}, {"id": 350751, "content": "这个词有什么梗", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279533}, {"id": 350753, "content": "\nPUA", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433133}, {"id": 350754, "content": "每个人都在看手机！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335747}, {"id": 350755, "content": "APP里出现的新功能，各种占热搜的娱乐新闻，新出的词梗，突然火的抖音神曲（新出的歌往往个人觉得实在是难听，却火地一塌糊涂，令人费解눈_눈）", "image": null, "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664029}, {"id": 350757, "content": "不认识的明星，当下的热门电视剧一个都不知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554968}, {"id": 352549, "content": "不追星，不喜欢偶像剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640758}, {"id": 351015, "content": "身边人都在买无人机玩航拍，我却对此毫无兴趣……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282756}, {"id": 350760, "content": "自己的腰包和飞涨的物价房价", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493266}, {"id": 350762, "content": "这里人说的大部分事，都不懂😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329728}, {"id": 350764, "content": "网红吵闹离婚……都是谁跟谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335610}, {"id": 350771, "content": "排行榜里的歌，很多自己都听不习惯，觉得不好听。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953682}, {"id": 350772, "content": "饭圈用语，缩写看不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369622}, {"id": 351541, "content": "从周围的人嘴里又蹦出来新词，我“？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666326}, {"id": 350775, "content": "举世皆浊我独清", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 350782, "content": "网上越来越多梗不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305934}, {"id": 350783, "content": "媒体上出现的明星大部分不认识", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601854}, {"id": 350784, "content": "听到那些国产电影/电视剧的名字，都好陌生啊…以前至少能混个耳熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333758}, {"id": 350786, "content": "看着某某明星，竟然一脸懵逼，who ？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181225}, {"id": 350787, "content": "网上热搜都和我没半点关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359635}, {"id": 352328, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 350794, "content": "00后开始生出20后，而我这个90后还是单身狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674249}, {"id": 351053, "content": "那种再丑不过的字体，突然间占据了电视节目，商品广告，商店招牌，甚至香港游行示威标语。低级审美！误人子弟！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662107}, {"id": 350799, "content": "看到小鲜肉A，这不是小鲜肉A吗\n看到小鲜肉B，这不是小鲜肉A吗\n…\n看到小鲜肉Z，这不是小鲜肉A吗\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1430596}, {"id": 350800, "content": "三年了还没有涨工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573201}, {"id": 350802, "content": "最大的脱节是已经开始害怕接触那些不懂的事物了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155179}, {"id": 351058, "content": "新声代歌手都不认识了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1669651}, {"id": 350804, "content": "热搜上的都是谁？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667430}, {"id": 350805, "content": "停留在零几年喜好\n思维跟不上时代了\n越来越看不懂所谓的潮流", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652167}, {"id": 350806, "content": "完全不玩微博..", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844519}, {"id": 350807, "content": "饭圈的字母文都是啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440729}, {"id": 350813, "content": "现在的明星网红\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838273}, {"id": 350814, "content": "网红一个都不认识，简写的拼音首字母一个都看不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674877}, {"id": 350817, "content": "早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668570}, {"id": 350820, "content": "开始对APP的一些新版本跟新推出功能感到疲倦，升级提示别跳出来，莫挨老子！", "image": "img/option/option/201912171732270jtzZ6ouQ4BYiwqW", "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675342}, {"id": 350823, "content": "看不懂热搜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528961}, {"id": 351082, "content": "微博热搜前面那些人都不知道那些人是谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310603}, {"id": 350828, "content": "从来不玩抖音", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107293}]}